{
  "stem": "15082.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But in later years, it did come out, because even-- not only were the children resentful.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But even the teachers that I had, when I look back some of them were very, very harsh, because I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had to tolerate me in school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- but we paid a big price, almost get beat up on the way home from school, and that sort of stuff.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was an ongoing thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The best that I can remember is I probably must have been already 10 years old.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they played a game where you stand around in a circle-- that's during recess in school.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the teacher would take off his belt, and put it in the back of-- everybody had to keep their hands on their back.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And if he put it into you, and if you didn't run fast enough, you got hit.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And somehow or other, the belt always never landed in the Jewish kids' hands.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we came home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we complained.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And what is outstanding in my mind is one of the-- my friend's brother, which was a older fellow, had just gotten back from serving in the Polish army.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He heard about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And his brother was in school with me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he came out to watch this game.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it infuriated him to such a point that he got into a fight with the teacher, tell him that, you know, it's unforgettable to what's going on.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they got into a shoving match.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the teacher had brought him up on charges.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The police came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And it wounded up in a trial.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But the judge understood that what-- what the teacher did too.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he dismissed the charges against the-- my friend's brother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By and large, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
